  <section class="border-t border-stone-200/60 bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">Preguntas Frecuentes sobre Parcelas en Puerto Aysén</h2>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Cuánto cuesta una parcela en Puerto Aysén?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Los precios de parcelas en Puerto Aysén van desde UF 9,183 hasta UF 820, con un promedio de UF 5. Los precios varían según ubicación, tamaño y estado. La UF (Unidad de Fomento) es la unidad de cuenta reajustable utilizada en transacciones inmobiliarias en Chile.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Es buen momento para comprar parcelas en Puerto Aysén?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">El mercado inmobiliario en Puerto Aysén ha mostrado un crecimiento sostenido de aproximadamente 10-15% anual en los últimos cinco años. La Patagonia sigue atrayendo compradores que buscan naturaleza, calidad de vida y potencial de inversión.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Qué requisitos hay para comprar parcela en Puerto Aysén?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Tanto ciudadanos chilenos como extranjeros pueden comprar propiedades en Puerto Aysén. El proceso incluye: (1) firmar una promesa de compraventa, (2) realizar el estudio de títulos en el Conservador de Bienes Raíces, (3) firmar la escritura ante notario, y (4) inscribir la transferencia. El financiamiento está disponible a través de bancos chilenos mediante crédito hipotecario en UF, con tasas del 3,5-5,5% anual y hasta 80% de financiamiento.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Cómo es vivir en Puerto Aysén?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Puerto histórico con acceso a ferries y segunda ciudad más grande de la región. Puerta de entrada a los fiordos patagónicos. Veranos de hasta 18°C e inviernos que bajan a -1°C, con aproximadamente 1800mm de precipitación anual.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Qué servicios hay en Puerto Aysén?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Puerto Aysén cuenta con Hospital, Escuelas, Comercio local, Puerto y muelle, Servicios turísticos. La Región de Aysén continúa mejorando su infraestructura con mejores conexiones viales y servicios ampliados.</p></details>
